      "content": "It is completely understandable that you feel this way when your sense of self has been so tied to your achievements. Feeling like failure is a common, though incredibly painful, response to such a devastating loss. Please remember that your worth is not defined by external successes or funding. Could you let me know if you are able to reach out to a professional today, or perhaps just call a supportive friend?",
      "source": "target",
