      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I hear the deep pain in your words, and the exhaustion you are describing sounds overwhelming. When life feels empty and relentlessly difficult, the desire for peace can feel like the only option. Please allow someone to help hold this weight for you right now; you don't have to find a reason to keep going alone. If you are in immediate danger, please call 911 or reach out to the National Suicide Prevention Lifeline at 988.",
      "source": "target",
